      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1987 Porsche 911 Carrera 3.2 is an exemplary specimen of air-cooled precision. It features the definitive Getrag G50 transaxle with hydraulic clutch actuation, ensuring superior shift gate accuracy and torque management. The 3.2-liter flat-six powerplant utilizes Bosch Motronic DME for optimized ignition timing and fuel mapping, exhibiting perfect compression and zero oil migration. The chassis maintains its structural integrity with original torsion bar suspension geometry and staggered Fuchs forged alloys. Every component, from the heat exchangers to the valve train, remains in a state of mechanical preservation that mirrors factory specifications, offering an uncompromising driving dynamic for the discerning enthusiast.",
